original_title: Gowok The Ins and Outs of A Woman’s Body
overview: A father who expects his son to be a gentleman, to be a real man through the Pergowokan process, (pergowokan is an old Javanese tradition in 1400 that has been lost now, that tradition is where a father finds an adult woman for his son, to teach about how to please a woman, and everything related to a woman)
title: Gowok The Ins and Outs of A Woman’s Body
